summary: An Ordinance repealing Ordinance No. 25316, entitled "An Ordinance authorizing and directing the dismissal of the Leary Avenue condemnation suit, under Ordinance No. 21303, Cause No. 69865, in so far as the same affects the taking only of certain portions of lots one (1) to five (5), inclusive, block sixty-eight (68), in Gilman Park," approved October 13, 1910.
